### ─── إنشاء تصنيف رئيسي ─────────────────────────────────────

### Create Category: Electronics
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "icon": "Laptop",
  "color": "#2563eb",
  "order": 1,
  "translations": [
    { "locale": "ar", "name": "إلكترونيات", "description": "كل ما يخص الأجهزة الإلكترونية" },
    { "locale": "en", "name": "Electronics", "description": "All electronic devices" }
  ]
}

### Create Category: Fashion
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "icon": "Shirt",
  "color": "#db2777",
  "order": 2,
  "translations": [
    { "locale": "ar", "name": "موضة", "description": "الأزياء والملابس" },
    { "locale": "en", "name": "Fashion", "description": "Clothing and accessories" }
  ]
}

### ─── إنشاء تصنيف فرعي ─────────────────────────────────────

### Create Subcategory: Mobile Phones (parent: electronics)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "PUT_ELECTRONICS_ID_HERE",
  "icon": "Smartphone",
  "color": "#2563eb",
  "order": 1,
  "translations": [
    { "locale": "ar", "name": "هواتف محمولة", "description": "جوالات وتبلت" },
    { "locale": "en", "name": "Mobile Phones", "description": "Smartphones and tablets" }
  ]
}

### ─── جلب التصنيفات مع Pagination ──────────────────────────

### Get All Categories (page 1, default limit)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Get All Categories (page 1, limit 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: en

### Get Categories with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?search=إلكترون
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Active Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Categories by Parent
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?parentId=PUT_PARENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ─── جلب تصنيف بواسطة Slug ────────────────────────────────

### Get Category by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/slug/electronics
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ─── جلب تصنيف بواسطة ID ──────────────────────────────────

### Get Category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/PUT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: en

### ─── تعديل تصنيف ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Update Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/PUT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "#16a34a",
  "translations": [
    { "locale": "ar", "name": "إلكترونيات محدثة", "description": "وصف محدث" },
    { "locale": "en", "name": "Updated Electronics", "description": "Updated description" }
  ]
}

### ─── ربط صورة بالتصنيف ────────────────────────────────────

### Attach Image to Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/PUT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE/image
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileId": "PUT_FILE_ID_HERE"
}

### ─── إلغاء تنشيط تصنيف ────────────────────────────────────

### Deactivate Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/PUT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ─── إعادة ترتيب تصنيف ────────────────────────────────────

### Reorder Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/PUT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order": 10
}

### ─── حذف تصنيف ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete Category (will fail if has children or products)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/PUT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
